### Create an organization quota

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/organization_quotas" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-type: application/json" \
  -d '{
        "name": "production"
      }'
```

```
